beIN SPORTS 3.title: Sevilla vs Athletic Club - Spanish LaLiga 2025/26 - Week 21

beIN SPORTS 3.title: Rangers vs Ludogorets Razgrad - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD7

beIN SPORTS 3.original_title: Fenerbahce vs Aston Villa - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD7
beIN SPORTS 3.title: Fenerbahce vs Aston Villa - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD7
